>\n犯法就報 好簡單！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔止食堂啦<br />\n基本上全香港工廈都唔係工業用途<br />\n絶大部分做寫字樓或劏成細寫字樓分租<br />\n部分做商業賣野<br />\n部分做食堂<br />\n仲有迷你倉<br />\n<br />\n照正法例應該淨係工業用途<br />\n咁全香港工廈應該吉曬<br />\n因為香港根本已經冇工業<br />\n<br />\n到時候小商戶想做生意又冇地方做<br />\n閒置工廈又擺係度養老鼠<br />\n咁係咪好結果?</blockquote><br />\n說好的活化工廈呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07fedc2630112c904ac95315a8673310dd7aaae","tid":333310,"uid":84123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:52:17.000Z","msg":"走去報串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁咪抵香港人去到邊都係食大家樂大快活美心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f259d21a195de5ff3f2f8f1a9a94d3b1ad67cb30","tid":333310,"uid":116975,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:53:29.000Z","msg":"樓豬我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cc65fb3511e25b9d789be045724ad63decfa17","tid":333310,"uid":37717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:59:59.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪比工廈既餐廳炒魷唔岔氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f69bbf5782aa3ab82a2e786ca15739f0e25190","tid":333310,"uid":38757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>工廈食堂就無事</blockquote><br />\n好多西餐廳/cafe 係咪報得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算食堂牌都好似只可以提供食物俾大廈入面既人<br />\n<br />\n果啲西餐廳 cafe<br />\n報唔報得就真係一間間計啦<br />\n其實有好多都冇牌或者唔齊牌 就算街鋪都係<br />\n如果佢啲牌照齊就例外<br />\n<br />\n不過今時今日 做老闆都只係幫個業主打工<br />\n如果唔過份就俾條生路人行啦</blockquote><br />\nching 有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個岩, 我間唔中會去觀塘食野<br />\n工廈開鋪好多都係幫業主打工架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見有D呢期都好多工廈鋪執....<br />\n工廈鋪買野食好就好在平D , 多D 特色野食, <br />\n其實想食新款D既野, 去觀塘係一個好既選擇"},{"pid":"d60570182f22777cd97bed228f4c56d4167dd443","tid":333310,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"合法"},{"pid":"2c8a850686e6f234842e4f98144d0000c38c02b0","tid":333310,"uid":22270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:08:20.000Z","msg":"有牌咪合"},{"pid":"2b5c361dee3531ca1d9c04e4304518eb331e4561","tid":333310,"uid":22270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:08:35.000Z","msg":"HA轉做餐廳都無事"},{"pid":"7146e069443b2445d532ee765a2e1a11f791fc72","tid":333310,"uid":20518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"香港人魚蛋論真係入曬骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917b25b77b93d1875051ef0d2159c694506846bf","tid":333310,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"仲有d party room 合法咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc8ad63a3ff1ff0b8b7740fb45d7b089dc2a1ca","tid":333310,"uid":21309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"無啦啦走去搞鳩人做乜春 搞到其他人lunch冇啖好食"},{"pid":"beb4af22c23d3875d1955691f6a72a8380a3ff86","tid":333310,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"記得有個消防話工廈搞餐廳/音樂會, 人太多會危險<br />\n但係明明以前工廈都好多人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5c6fc82ded1f3d304621edb0d8d6ec8a4b4feb","tid":333310,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得有個消防話工廈搞餐廳/音樂會, 人太多會危險<br />\n但係明明以前工廈都好多人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩樣性質唔同<br />\n工廠/食堂有曬安全措施 攞正牌 呢啲小事<br />\n有啲餐廳/音樂會 唔合規格會好危險 個啲就要小心<br />\n但最大問題係政府個條例好out"},{"pid":"8ae21e0629bd3f3a01c4db46e7e8efd644c939d3","tid":333310,"uid":57914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>走去報串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁咪抵香港人去到邊都係食大家樂大快活美心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n工廈餐廳犯法呀 on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5d1de7cf9fe5e0303aba89ed4015f889d1d7c1","tid":333310,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主你想做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部大商場/領展場都有一式一樣連鎖食店<br />\n難得工廈有d  平價或特色野食<br />\n你又睇唔過眼想搞鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n犯法就報 好簡單！</blockquote><br />\n支持！"},{"pid":"3db3448b18ae2903131e2035bceb49190dc801f7","tid":333310,"uid":33829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:34:22.000Z","msg":"又係冇腦嘅戇鳩仔<br />\n連登真係咩人都有"},{"pid":"fe1f8020de8bbce1d6b07070f48895ab27275a30","tid":333310,"uid":114271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"又係呢d犯法就報嘅on9仔<br />\n記住舉報最所有BT狗，小販檔，踩單車載人嘅撚樣喎<br />\n睇你到時做唔做人民公敵 屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n係香港生存已經難，仲要遇著你呢挺食飽飯冇屎痾嘅柒碌真係喊三聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbcb7f6bb06b8e3669fc85230fbfcb5966ca08a8","tid":333310,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:39:38.000Z","msg":"係連登永遠唔好屌小店呀<br />\n會比人話冇人情味架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443ccf26d8efb0c6d6ca78ad1b5f001c6a3bfeac","tid":333310,"uid":128869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"法律=/=正確<br />\n犯法都唔等於唔正確<br />\n係守護法律